=====决赛=====
这场比赛对阵双方分别是东道主西班牙队和卫冕冠军苏联队。西班牙依靠佩雷达和马塞利诺的的两粒进球赢下了比赛<ref>{{cite news |url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/feature?id=530733&cc=4716 |title=European Nations Cup 1964 |work=ESPNSoccernet.com |publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |date=1 May 2008 |first=John |last=Brewin |accessdate=28 January 2013 |archive-date=2008-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080607022613/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/feature?id=530733&cc=4716 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

